    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Pat your<strong> capers </strong>dry<strong> </strong>with kitchen paper</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> capers</strong> to the pan and cook for 6-7 min or until crispy, then season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Once crispy, transfer the<strong> crispy capers</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
