    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in<strong> </strong>250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[350ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>stock</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
