      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and<strong> diced pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until golden and crisp</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
