      "instruction": "<p>Once the lardons are crispy, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Once slightly softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and<strong> chopped tomato </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until the tomato has completely softened</p>",
