      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving 80ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [100ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [120ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
