    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomato has completely softened, add the <strong>stock</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 7-8 min or until the sauce has thickened and everything's completely tender – this is your <strong>tomatoey bacon & pepper sauce</strong></p><p>Stir the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong> through the sauce with the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomatoey night bacon & pepper spaghetti</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Keep the sauce and pasta separate!</span></strong></p>",
